  "texts": [
    "The terms \"mathematics\" (frequency = 23), \"technology\" (frequency = 21) and \"problem solving\"/\"students\" (frequency = 17) were also among the commonly recurring keywords.",
    "Table 1 delineates the top 25 keywords based on frequency of repetition.",
    "www.richtmann.org Vol 15 No 1 January 2025 137 An examination of author keywords in the selected scholarly works revealed a recurring presence of terms including \"geogebra\", \"dynamic geometry environment\", \"geometry\", \"mathematics education\", \"teaching\" and \"mathematics\".",
    "These terms reflect a thematic correspondence with the research corpus and the objective of this study, which scrutinized the pattern of GeoGebra application in the field of mathematics education.",
    "Moreover, keywords such as \"problem-solving\", \"visualization\", \"reasoning\", \"functions\", \"calculus\", \"modelling\", \"argumentation\", \"augmented reality\" and \"conceptual understanding\" shed light on specific mathematical topics and pedagogical methods for which GeoGebra was applied."
